{"tid":1188733,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人間性器 NMB48白間美瑠澳洲滑浪晒半球","createTime":"2019-06-06T12:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T16:51:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2233985b69494aff7049638e334c2f7ed58c3f04","tid":1188733,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"日本女團NMB48的21歲主將白間美瑠，2010年入行加入NMB48，翌年升格成為成員，2017年開始擔任NMB單曲主唱一職，經過接近9年的磨練，今個月19日終於推出首本個人寫真集《LOVE RUSH》。<br />\n<br />\n寫真集在澳洲黃金海岸拍攝，白間除了穿水着騷性感，以及穿白恤衫中門大開騷晒半球之外，更標榜她天真爛漫和熱愛運動的一面，平時有做Gym及攀石的她，在當地挑戰滑浪，以及乘坐越野車欣賞美麗的海岸，展示她可愛和自信一面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/photo/bkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190606171101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190606171101&h=58306c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/photo/bkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190606171101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190606171101&h=d9150978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/photo/bkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190606171101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190606171101&h=e80d3e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/photo/bkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190606171101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190606165738696-0606_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190606171101&h=69285b28&s={SIZE}\" /